      <title>胡塞武装对商业航运的袭击不断升级，伤亡人数不断增加</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-24/houthi-attacks-on-commercial-shipping-ramp-up-and-get-deadlier</link>
      <description><![CDATA[胡塞武装分子正在袭击也门附近的商船，其袭击力度不断加大，有时甚至致命，暴露出以美国为首的联盟在平息全球一些最重要水道上的暴力事件方面的能力有限。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-24/houthi-attacks-on-commercial-shipping-ramp-up-and-get-deadlier</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 24 Jun 2024 13:37:43 GMT</pubDate>
