      <title>英国大选：巴德诺克和雷诺兹就脱欧问题发生冲突</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-06-24/uk-election-badenoch-and-reynolds-clash-over-brexit</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在周一彭博社的选举辩论中，英国商务大臣凯米·巴德诺赫和影子商务大臣乔纳森·雷诺兹就英国脱欧后如何缓解与欧盟的贸易摩擦发生了冲突。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-06-24/uk-election-badenoch-and-reynolds-clash-over-brexit</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 24 Jun 2024 13:22:42 GMT</pubDate>
